title: #2 $SPELL Farming Reduction and Supply Burn Proposal
body:
Abracadabra has become a force of nature, we are seeing usage explode, and MIM peg being extremely strong. For this reason I propose to burn and reduce 20% of the SPELL that has been allocated to farming rewards. This marketing budget is no longer required, the team and treasury does not need this allocation.

To read the details about amounts to be burned and more please refer to the medium post here: https://abracadabramoney.medium.com/spell-farming-reduction-and-supply-burn-proposal-9e6e0dfdb78f
author: 0x8A7f7C5b556B1298a74c0e89df46Eba117A2F6c1
